Package hu.nye.model

Class Transaction

java.lang.Object
hu.nye.model.Transaction
@Entity public class Transaction extends Object
Represents a transaction entity in the application. This entity stores information about a transaction, including the transaction date, total amount, associated customer, and the list of products involved.
